e or challenge a friend.","popularity":1.0,"games":[75962,46815,75964,75858,75857,75853,68609,55058,50726,50704],"tags":[268435460],"category":0,"genres":[4],"first_release_date":990144000000,"platforms":[7],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":7,"date":990144000000,"region":8,"human":"2001-May-18","y":2001,"m":5}]},{"id":43913,"name":"Thunder Force V: Perfect System","slug":"thunder-force-v-perfect-system","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/thunder-force-v-perfect-system","created_at":1499166053572,"updated_at":1515717673641,"summary":"In a grim future where a once-benevolent alien technology has turned against humanity, only a ragtag group of ace pilots can save the Earth from total annihilation. Code name: Thunder Force! Witness the first 32-bit installment of the massively popular shooter series! Five spectacular weapons with multiple power-up levels let you blast through waves of metallic predators, and look good doing it. A constant barrage of innovative enemies keeps you intrigued while you struggle to stay alive. A speaker-imploding soundtrack has your foot tapping as your fingers are mashing. Unbelievable rendered cutscenes draw, no-DRAG you kicking and screaming into the action. Put simply, it's the ultimate hardcore gaming blast-o-rama!","collection":863,"popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[25311,33603,36962,55888,65827,32283,18623,29173,55308,36718],"tags":[18,268435461,268435469,268435471,268435488,536871937,536875284,1073741828],"category":0,"player_perspectives":[4],"game_modes":[1],"keywords":[1025,4372],"themes":[18],"genres":[5],"first_release_date":907200000000,"platforms":[7],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":7,"date":907200000000,"region":8,"human":"1998-Oct-01","y":1998,"m":10}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/omixelqfjffzfwzzoxw8.jpg","cloudinary_id":"omixelqfjffzfwzzoxw8","width":369,"height":300},"websites":[]},{"id":43914,"name":"Vanguard Bandits","slug":"vanguard-bandits","url":"https://www.igdb.c