ibulations involved with school, friends and parents. The book series by author K.A. Applegate has more than 32 million copies in print and there is a popular TV show airing on Nickelodeon. \n \nIn the PlayStation game Animorphs - Shattered Reality, the characters find themselves in a time warp. You must help them gather the shards of the Time Matrix Crystal and restore the timeline back to normal. You can play as any of the Animorphs as you battle The Yeerks and Visser 3.","collection":4937,"popularity":1.0,"games":[55752,27314,19448,25300,36950,36868,25311,19174,26766,68287],"tags":[1,18,268435464,268435487,536870915,536871882,536871939,536872961,536875055,536875073,536875088,536876353,536877029,536877236,536886150,536886151,536886153],"category":0,"keywords":[3,970,1027,2049,4143,4161,4176,5441,6117,6324,15238,15239,15241],"themes":[1,18],"genres":[8,31],"first_release_date":970790400000,"platforms":[7],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":7,"date":970790400000,"region":8,"human":"2000-Oct-06","y":2000,"m":10}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/phlokeraoxkyusnljwsc.jpg","cloudinary_id":"phlokeraoxkyusnljwsc","width":500,"height":500},"esrb":{"rating":3}},{"id":43928,"name":"American Pool","slug":"american-pool","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/american-pool","created_at":1499166246777,"updated_at":1515798118003,"summary":"With American Pool, publisher Mud Duck brings a budget-priced virtual 3D billiards presentation with three modes of gameplay to the PlayStation. In Training mode, players learn the controls and various pool techniques by solving tasks and problems, while Pocket Game mode offers five types of pool including 9-Ball, 8-Ball, Basic, Rotation and 14-1 Rack. The final mode, Pool Contest, is a 9-Ball bracketed tournament in which players create their own character and level up with special shots and techniques as they advance through the pairings. \n \nExamples of special skills that can be earned include Low Tech (adds 