 to the Legendary Edition, contains the cutscenes from Halo: Combat Evolved and Halo 2 in chronological order, with optional developer commentary featuring Joseph Staten, Martin O'Donnell, and Jason Jones. Also included on the disc is a guide to the 7 Steps to World Domination plan, included in a short history of Bungie, as well as a documentary chronicling Cortana voice actor Jen Taylor as she learns about the Bungie fan community. Also included was an episode of This Spartan Life which included footage made in Halo 3, and two episodes of Red vs Blue, \"The Call\" and a special edition of Red vs Blue Episode I. Included in the special edition of Red vs Blue Episode I was a short mockumentary about the time leading up to the creation of the series. Also on this disc is the expanded digital Bestiarum and also the surround sound test carried over from Halo 2.","collection":173,"franchise":137,"franchises":[137],"popularity":1.333333333333333,"version_parent":987,"version_title":"Legendary Edition","games":[103281,28029,103298,103020,103301,90099,86478,83728,27011,76722],"tags":[1,18,39,268435461,1073741826,1073741825],"developers":[620],"publishers":[53],"category":3,"player_perspectives":[1,2],"game_modes":[1,2,4],"themes":[1,18,39],"genres":[5],"first_release_date":1190678400000,"platforms":[12],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":12,"date":1190678400000,"region":2,"human":"2007-Sep-25","y":2007,"m":9}],"alternative_names":[{"name":"Halo 3 - Legendary Edition","comment":"Acronym"}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/jclndhmhrrdu3b9qpday.jpg","cloudinary_id":"jclndhmhrrdu3b9qpday","width":450,"height":229}},{"id":43956,"name":"Halo Wars: Limited Edition","slug":"halo-wars-limited-edition","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/halo-wars-limited-edition","created_at":1499168434079,"updated_at":1515493990875,"summary":"Purchase of Halo Wars Limited Edition comes with the following: \n \nHalo Wars game disc inside a special metal two-sided case