 friends to go hunting for animals. You can go spear-fishing, take out rabbits with your sling, or go for bigger prey like Sabertooth Tigers. And if you are up to the challenge, you can get a group of friends together into a hunting party and you can try your hand at hunting mammoths! Be careful though, the bigger the animals, the more dangerous they are!","hypes":1,"popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[28465,34919,33603,36962,55888,44087,65827,28277,32283,55308],"tags":[268435469,268435488,1073741825],"developers":[14928],"game_engines":[553],"category":0,"player_perspectives":[1],"game_modes":[1,2],"genres":[13,32],"first_release_date":1526947200000,"status":4,"platforms":[6],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":6,"date":1526947200000,"region":8,"human":"2018-May-22","y":2018,"m":5}],"screenshots":[{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/ip5bw1fkaxhh8a18amef.jpg","cloudinary_id":"ip5bw1fkaxhh8a18amef","width":1920,"height":1080},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/rnna2b7qyqapb3pgzwll.jpg","cloudinary_id":"rnna2b7qyqapb3pgzwll","width":1280,"height":720},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/stnzj3r2umy165rljv8f.jpg","cloudinary_id":"stnzj3r2umy165rljv8f","width":1920,"height":1080},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/hqm5zcfixxdqoqpwnc7c.jpg","cloudinary_id":"hqm5zcfixxdqoqpwnc7c","width":1920,"height":1080},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/lxo8q0muykxvjo9vdbou.jpg","cloudinary_id":"lxo8q0muykxvjo9vdbou","width":1920,"height":1080}],"videos":[{"name":"Trailer","video_id":"cvRqW-cIAn4"}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/qriz4szk2jdiwt0vyyaw.jpg","cloudinary_id":"qriz4szk2jdiwt0vyyaw","width":600,"height":800},"websites":[{"category":1,"url":"https://store.steampowered.com/app/342910/Vantage_Primitive_Survival_Game/"},{"category":6,"url":"https://www.twitch.tv/directory/game/Vantage%3A%20Primitive%20Survival%20Game"},{"category":5,"url":"https://twitter.co