ame - our heroes travel the world, visit towns, villages, dungeons and gather clues. Combats are turned-based and are randomly triggered throughout the game, and their sole purpose is to gain experience points and to level up. Magic has also its place in the game and the player can combine spells to trigger more powerful combo-attacks.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"category":0,"genres":[12],"first_release_date":739756800000,"platforms":[19],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":19,"date":739756800000,"region":8,"human":"1993-Jun-11","y":1993,"m":6}]},{"id":44411,"name":"Zen-Nippon GT Senshuken","slug":"zen-nippon-gt-senshuken","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/zen-nippon-gt-senshuken","created_at":1499424433347,"updated_at":1516779836896,"summary":"Zen-Nippon GT Senshuken (\"All-Japan GT Championship\") is a racing game published by Banpresto and Kaneko, and is part of Kaneko's All-Japan Grand Touring Car Championship series based on the real-life circuit. The game rapidly switches angles depending on the direction the player is driving, often moving between horizontal, vertical and diagonal perspectives.","popularity":1.0,"games":[38362,79063,38335,42277,49004,46885,42628,42266,42358,58785],"tags":[268435466,536873390,536874337,536875054,536875069,536875117,536875140,536875955,536876108,536876698,536876786],"category":0,"keywords":[2478,3425,4142,4157,4205,4228,5043,5196,5786,5874],"genres":[10],"first_release_date":814924800000,"platforms":[19],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":19,"date":814924800000,"region":8,"human":"1995-Oct-29","y":1995,"m":10}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/rfgaw3ib6vjz4gstr3j0.jpg","cloudinary_id":"rfgaw3ib6vjz4gstr3j0","width":299,"height":543}},{"id":44412,"name":"Kinnikuman: Dirty Challenger","slug":"kinnikuman-dirty-challenger","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/kinnikuman-dirty-challenger","created_at":1499424456007,"updated_at":1515780702123,"summary":"Kinnikuman: Dirty Challenger is a wrest