ctions that can be performed by a particular character. The more actions performed (and thus, more RAPs expended) during a turn, the longer you'll have to wait for your next chance to act. When attacking, an interactive gauge appears that does damage based upon where the slider is stopped. Stopping it at the very end will result in greater damage dealt to the enemy. Wait too long however and the slider will return to the beginning.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[75813,5613,49414,25636,25311,75398,18811,36608,74929,21842],"tags":[268435468,268435471],"category":0,"genres":[12,15],"first_release_date":1011484800000,"platforms":[7],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":7,"date":1011484800000,"region":8,"human":"2002-Jan-20","y":2002,"m":1}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/x8t66qa6zqaqunlfhqzy.jpg","cloudinary_id":"x8t66qa6zqaqunlfhqzy","width":911,"height":868}},{"id":45224,"name":"NASCAR Racing","slug":"nascar-racing","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/nascar-racing","created_at":1499458200654,"updated_at":1500536478362,"summary":"The game presents three different game modes: Arcade Race, Simulation Race, and Simulation Testing. While the Arcade Race mode let's the player jump right into the fray after choosing their difficulty level (either rookie,veteran, or ace), the Simulation Race mode features a lot more customization options for the player to take into consideration.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[23314,18699,76259,103018,101535,101205,101142,101087,100902,100844],"tags":[268435466],"category":0,"genres":[10],"first_release_date":846633600000,"platforms":[7],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":7,"date":846633600000,"region":8,"human":"1996-Oct-30","y":1996,"m":10}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/croudhsnqdyoeaj8lbxd.jpg","cloudinary_id":"croudhsnqdyoeaj8lbxd","width":1000,"height":968}},{"id":45225,"name":"Destrega","slug":"destrega","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/destrega"