33333333,"games":[44242,54662,18623,22470,29173,26145,22425,55689,55590,70168],"tags":[268435469,268435470,536871212,536872060,536872078,536876641],"category":0,"keywords":[300,1148,1166,5729],"genres":[13,14],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/aa2a5julojpvvux0vney.jpg","cloudinary_id":"aa2a5julojpvvux0vney","width":352,"height":296}},{"id":45324,"name":"Eric \u0026 The Floaters","slug":"eric-and-the-floaters","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/eric-and-the-floaters","created_at":1499504360957,"updated_at":1500536518189,"summary":"You must press any key to start the game. It will then ask you if you want to use Keyboard or Joystick. After that section, the game will start. \n \nThe aim of each level of the game is to kill all of the floaters, the orange/magenta ball-like things that roam the maze. To do this you have one weapon on your side - an infinite supply of bombs. When you drop a bomb, they are automatically primed, and will explode after just a few seconds. \n \nSo to kill the baddies you must get close enough to them to within the range of the bomb, drop it, and quickly run around a corner to make sure you too are not caught in the explosion. The bombs will destroy any floaters that are caught in the blast, and also certain sections of wall that are in the way, reducing the \nplaying area to open landscape. \n \nMore and more floaters are added each level, and the game does get quite difficult. You can also only drop one bomb at a time.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[36608,2940,40524,34919,71581,29660,1070,23175,76438,16468],"tags":[1],"category":0,"themes":[1]},{"id":45325,"name":"Spooked","slug":"spooked","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/spooked","created_at":1499504364196,"updated_at":1515676766059,"summary":"As an experienced ghoul-chaser, you think you can handle anything when you get a call to explore a haunted mansion. You soon realize that you're wrong, however, and you'll need all of your skills to deal with 384 screens of spookiness. \n \nIt's an arcade adventure, with ghosts to avoid as they cause your character to fall off course, sometimes down a screen or two. Collecting bugs and beetles allows you to use one of the cauldrons to produce spells to kill enemies. You have 4 minutes on each life, although more can be picked up from the many egg-timers around the screens. The game keeps track of your 'Scaredyness factor' and adjusts the game difficulty to help struggling players accordingly. \n \nThe eventual target is to collect items to turn into letters - earning enough of these allows you to play a Hangman game against the 'spooky old man'.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[25311,26145,22425,44242,34919,44076,54999,19290,54662,43130],"tags":[1,268435469,268435470,268435487,536871212,536872060,536872078,536876641],"category":0,"keywords":[300,1148,1166,5729],"themes":[1],"genres":[13,14,31]},{"id":45326,"name":"Saimazoom","slug":"saimazoom","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/saimazoom","created_at":1499504366012,"updated_at":1512987632022,"summary":"SAIMAZOOM es un video-juego aventura que se desarrolla en un paraje perdido de \nuna selva extraña. \n \nTu misión es explorar la selva descubriendo sus peligros y secretos que no \nvamos a desvelarte pues el juego perdería parte de su aliciente. \n \nLo único que revelamos es la razón de que estés en la selva. \n \nDebes encontrar los cuatro sacos de SAIMAZOOM y regresar vivo con ellos al \npunto de partida.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[13189,71056,13629,55803,25222,41895,22425,70396,29730,11296],"tags":[536871939],"category":0,"keywords":[1027],"genres":[31],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/qewvyriw2gcwdrb4zcxf.jpg","cloudinary_id":"qewvyriw2gcwdrb4zcxf","width":303,"height":444}},{"id":45327,"name":"Marsport","slug":"marsport","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/marsport","created_at":1499504369504,"updated_at":1500536521312,"summary":"Marsport is the first (and ultimately only) game in an unfinished trilogy set in the 25th century. Humanity is at war with the Sept alien race, and they are now in a position to invade Earth, as they have the plans for their protective sphere. You play John Marsh, a soldier turned leader who must go to Mars and locate the original plans. \n \nMarsport uses the same game system as Tir Na Nog and Dun Darach, although a 3D effect is incorporated into the graphics. A single path is displayed on screen at a time, and the view is rotated at junctions. The Warriors and Warlords must be shot down using weaponry, making this Gargoyle's most action-driven adventure up to this point. \n \nThe Marsport is split into ten distinct sections with their own functions, such as Stores, Administration and Computers. There are robots to interact with, for gaining information or objects. Pairs of objects can be combined to manufacture new ones. A central computer locks out many sections until it can be found and disabled. You will have to shoot the Sept before they can touch you, and also be wary of Warden robots which may malfunction and mistake you for a Sept.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[14605,17469,75586,25130,43130,23175,28277,63734,29646,27266],"tags":[268435487],"category":0,"genres":[31]},{"id":45328,"name":"Evil Crown","slug":"evil-crown","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/evil-crown","created_at":1499504370914,"updated_at":1500536522655,"summary":"Bienvenidos a la Inglaterra Feudal. \nAcaba Ud. de convertirse en Barón alrededor del año 1200 d.C., en los días en los que no se elegía a nadie para nada. Exceptuando, quizás, al Prefecto de la Escuela. Se podía coger cualquier cosa si se era el primero en llegar y siendo, por regla general, más malintencionado que cualquier otro del valle. \n \nSi se era lo suficientemente malo con sus campesinos, si se vencía a suficientes Barones y si se desenvolvía bien en los Torneos Reales anuales, se podía llegar a ser Rey. ¡El mismísimo número Uno! Imagínese, puede que el actual poseedor de este \"empleo\" tenga un par de cosas que decir al respecto. (¡Odia a las personas con ambiciones sociales!). \n \nEste juego le da la oportunidad de intentar conseguir lo máximo. En una simulación animada muy gráfica Ud. podrá apoderarse de la Corona Malvada. Pero sólo si es lo bastante despiadado. Lo único que tiene que hacer es extender sus tierras, evitar que los campesinos se rebelen, amasar una fortuna y, lo más importante de todo, hacerlo bien en una amena secuencia de torneo a tiempo real. \n \nUa cosa más que debe Ud. saber - si lo intenta y falla, será ejecutado por traición. ¿Le gusta? \n \nLA CORONA MALVADA: UN JUEGO DE SIMULACION ANIMADA. LAS FUERZAS POLITICAS EN LA EDAD MEDIA. ¡FACIL DE JUGAR, MUY DIFICIL DE GANAR!","popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[11362,73075,9760,33603,36962,55888,65827,2015,32283,33383],"tags":[268435471],"category":0,"genres":[15]},{"id":45329,"name":"Skateball","slug":"skateball","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/skateball","created_at":1499504374101,"updated_at":1500536522939,"summary":"Skateball is a violent futuristic sport, part ice skating, part soccer. A match is played by two teams of three players each, one of them a goalkeeper, on an ice court with steel walls, and a single ball. The objective of Skateball is to score five goals or kill the three players of the opposite team. To achieve this, there are no rules and any kind of contact is allowed. There are several different courts with holes and other lethal obstacles. \n \nThe game can be played in single player vs. the computer, or two players against each other.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[6051,50457,50036,48599,47750,47589,46256,46089,45402,45221],"tags":[268435460,268435470],"category":0,"genres":[4,14],"first_release_date":570672000000,"platforms":[26],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":26,"date":570672000000,"region":8,"human":"1988-Feb-01","y":1988,"m":2}]},{"id":45330,"name":"Astro Clone","slug":"astro-clone","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/astro-clone","created_at":1499504389917,"updated_at":1500536523581,"summary":"A team of crack pilots, soldiers and technicians were assembled to form a group known as the Clone Warriors. For months they trained for an unknown mission. At the end the Space Commander himself arrived for their final briefing. The Clone Warriors were led to a large chamber resembling a hospital ward with rows of couches fronted by monitor screens. The cloning device lowered and the room lights dimmed. The advanced Sei computers combined the data from each of the Clone Warriors to produce the master image of the Astro-Clone. The monitors flickered to life to show the static image of the 24 Star-sectors. The combined mind of the Clone Warriors recognised Sol in the top left corner where 15 Clone Ships were ready to battle the Seiddab. Simultaneously the combined minds operated the control panels. A ship left the Sol sector and moved into Seiddab territory. The Astro-Clone invasion was underway.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"category":0},{"id":45331,"name":"Antiriad","slug":"antiriad","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/antiriad","created_at":1499504392135,"updated_at":1500536524193,"summary":"Tras el holocausto nuclear, los hombres supervivientes viven en tribus y no existe la tecnología. Esta precaria situación ha sido aprovechada por una raza de alienígenas para someter a la humanidad. La única esperanza del hombre es encontrar una antigua armadura, creada en la era atómica, cuyo tremendo poder una vez activada permitiría a los hombres enfrentarse al enemigo. \nPara activar la armadura deberemos insertar en ella cada una de las células de energía \nque están diseminadas por la montaña en la que los extraterrestres tienen su impenetrable base de operaciones.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"category":0},{"id":45332,"name":"RetroQuest","slug":"retroquest","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/retroquest","created_at":1499504393872,"updated_at":1500536524427,"summary":"A