dated_at":1500536552861,"popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[14605,17469,75586,25130,43130,23175,28277,63734,29646,27266],"tags":[268435487],"category":0,"genres":[31]},{"id":45365,"name":"Oracles Cave","slug":"oracles-cave","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/oracles-cave","created_at":1499504994270,"updated_at":1500536553551,"popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[14605,17469,75586,25130,43130,23175,28277,63734,29646,27266],"tags":[268435487],"category":0,"genres":[31]},{"id":45366,"name":"Mad Martha 2","slug":"mad-martha-2","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/mad-martha-2","created_at":1499504997411,"updated_at":1500536554223,"popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[14605,17469,75586,25130,43130,23175,28277,63734,29646,27266],"tags":[268435487],"category":0,"genres":[31]},{"id":45367,"name":"Mad Martha","slug":"mad-martha","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/mad-martha","created_at":1499505002020,"updated_at":1513004216137,"summary":"This (mostly) text adventure game places you in the role of hen-pecked hero, Henry Littlefellow. Seeking entertainment once in his life, your goal is to steal back your wages from your wife's purse and head off to the bright lights of the nearby casino (and other establishments) for a night of fun. Unfortunately, your axe-wielding maniac wife won't let things be that simple, and even escaping the house will be tricky without stumbling in the dark or waking the baby and alerting her to your sneaky plan. \n \nMad Martha is primarily a standard text adventure game, however the user is also presented with the odd arcade section (such as collecting £'s of money whilst avoiding the family cat, or dodging frogger-style across a road to go back home and collect the car keys), to break up the game flow. Getting into the casino leads you to the final challenge.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[23175,37022,55289,59516,13189,25222,25646,55803,42080,41895],"tags":[1,268435487,536871939],"category":0,"keywords":[1027],"themes":[1],"genres":[31]},{"id":45368,"name":"Krakatoa","slug":"krakatoa","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/krakatoa","created_at":1499505210869,"updated_at":1500536547261,"summary":"There are several thing you must do in this game. Your general \nobjective is to keep everybody and everything safe from the \nvolcano and the periodical air strikes. And the submarine. \n \nStarting on the left hand side of the playing area, the first \nisland is your base. This is where you start from, and if your \nhelicopter gets damaged, landing here will repair it. You can \nalso refuel from here as well. Should you also rescue any \npeople, this is where you must drop them of to gain the points. \nRescuing is done by lowering the rope and flying the end of it \ninto the men. Depending on how much rope you lower, you can \ncarry up to 5 people at once. When dropping them off, be careful \nthat you just lower the bottom person on the rope to level with \nthe ground - they will automatically climb off. If you go down \ntoo low you will kill them.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[76246,19341,28029,32902,24920,272,68287,10039,68142,36608],"tags":[1,268435461],"category":0,"themes":[1],"genres":[5]},{"id":45369,"name":"Beach Head 2: The Dictator Strikes Back","slug":"beach-head-2-the-dictator-strikes-back","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/beach-head-2-the-dictator-strikes-back","created_at":1499505216941,"updated_at":1513006175352,"summary":"Beach-Head II features the player pursuing the eponymous Dictator in several ways. There are four levels in the game. In the first level, called Attack, the player deploys soldiers along a path with walls to cover him from the dictator's gun. The objective is to destroy the gun. The second level involves rescuing the prisoners from deadly obstacles by clearing them with a gun. The third level's objective is to escape from the area by flying a helicopter with the prisoners out of the dictator's fortress. Finally the player and the dictator face off, on opposite cliffs, separated by water. To defeat him, the player must make him fall in the water by throwing knives at him. The Dictator tries to do the same to the player. \n \nIn one player mode there are three skill levels, harder modes resulting in faster movements and the computer opponent using better artificial intelligence. In two player mode, one player controls the usual side whilst his opponent controls the Dictator's forces. \n \nThis game was notable for using synthesized speech (courtesy of Electronic Speech Systems, then of Berkeley, California). Known for its deathly scream (also heard in Epyx's Impossible Mission), laughing, \"I'm hit\", \"Medic\", \"Hey! Don't shoot me\" and \"You can't hurt me\".","collection":4993,"popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[28751,28029,10039,76246,68287,19341,18088,68142,32902,36950],"tags":[1,268435461,536870913,536871510,536872285,536875171,536876408,536877281],"category":0,"keywords":[1,598,1373,4259,5496,6369],"themes":[1],"genres":[5],"alternative_names":[{"name":"Beach Head 2: The Dictator Strikes Back!","comment":"Other"}]},{"id":45370,"name":"Adventure D Espionage Island","slug":"adventure-d-espionage-island","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/adventure-d-espionage-island","created_at":1499505219986,"updated_at":1513087046257,"summary":"a text adventure game for the ZX Spectrum where the player controls a spy shot down while investigating an enemy stronghold","popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[13189,25222,55803,41895,22425,29730,11296,70396,19289,43130],"tags":[268435487,536871939,536873308],"category":0,"keywords":[1027,2396],"genres":[31]},{"id":45371,"name":"Ad Astra","slug":"ad-astra","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/ad-astra","created_at":1499505221798,"updated_at":1500536552488,"summary":"So, basically you had to blast away at incoming enemy ships and avoid crashing into planetoids. \n \nThe 3D effect of the planetoids coming towards you and the bad guys as they swooped 'out of' the screen was, at the time, pretty damn amazing. \n \nWith six lives to play with and seven stages to play through, the game offered some variety and also a pretty tough challenge. \n \nFive different types of aliens attacked in eight different formations, firing two types of lasers at you. \n \nThis was followed by a minefield stage where you had to destroy streams of rotating mines before they moved to close to your craft. \n \nThen come those pesky spinning saucers firing at you as they span across the gameplay area. These had to be hit several times to ensure destruction. \n \nThe last phase was a 'Way Station'. A security code appeared for the next Way Station, and as the station appeared the player had remember this code and then input it correctly.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[76246,19341,28029,32902,24920,272,68287,10039,68142,36608],"tags":[1,268435461],"category":0,"themes":[1],"genres":[5]},{"id":45372,"name":"Zen","slug":"zen","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/zen","created_at":1499505225553,"updated_at":1500511150455,"popularity":1.333333333333333,"category":0},{"id":45373,"name":"Intergalactic Cage Match","slug":"intergalactic-cage-match","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/intergalactic-cage-match","created_at":1499505227662,"updated_at":1500536554214,"summary":"Fight for your life against the best in the Universe in this fast paced intergalactic wrestling match which puts you in the ring with 6 of the toughest characters you could ever wish to meet!","popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[75962,46815,75964,75858,75857,75853,68609,55058,50726,50704],"tags":[268435460],"category":0,"genres":[4],"first_release_date":541641600000,"platforms":[26],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":26,"date":541641600000,"region":8,"human":"1987-Mar-02","y":1987,"m":3}]},{"id":45374,"name":"Zona 0","slug":"zona-0","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/zona-0","created_at":1499505229619,"updated_at":1513068840485,"summary":"Zona 0 es un videojuego del tipo arcade realizado por la compañía