al, and gave him her jewel. Once Astal and Jerado were dealt with, Antowas went back to sleep. \nHowever, Geist was still free, and Quartilia was not restored from the changes Jerado wrought. From his prison on the moon, Astal witnessed Geist kidnap Leda again. Consumed with the need to protect her, he freed himself and returned to Quartilia. Now Astal journeys in search of Leda through a Quartilia transformed by Jerado's dark design, along with a strange bird who for some reason just won't leave him alone...","popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[1070,1073,1188,10039,36608,74863,1066,34919,51485,26848],"tags":[1,268435464],"category":0,"themes":[1],"genres":[8],"first_release_date":814752000000,"platforms":[32],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":32,"date":814752000000,"region":8,"human":"1995-Oct-27","y":1995,"m":10}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/keyonxzdiffrbpa3pecl.jpg","cloudinary_id":"keyonxzdiffrbpa3pecl","width":1529,"height":2156}},{"id":45496,"name":"Andretti Racing","slug":"andretti-racing","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/andretti-racing","created_at":1499508828746,"updated_at":1500536669787,"summary":"Andretti Racing is a Formula One Racing game, developed by Press Start Inc. and published by Electronic Arts, which was released in 1996.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"category":0,"genres":[10],"first_release_date":823132800000,"platforms":[32],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":32,"date":823132800000,"region":8,"human":"1996-Feb-01","y":1996,"m":2}]},{"id":45497,"name":"Actua Golf","slug":"actua-golf","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/actua-golf","created_at":1499508832021,"updated_at":1500536671214,"summary":"Actua Golf is a golf simulation with full 3D terrain and characters. It comes with two courses to play at (country and tropical), customizable characters and multi-view shot tracking and action replays. \n \nActua Golf uses similar game controls as older golf titles did. With a swing meter, where you