s are visible on New Year's Day, and loading the game on April Fool's Day results in Reala replacing Nights as the playable character.","franchise":1060,"franchises":[1060],"popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[1070,41118,38305,1073,1188,89495,51942,51247,51203,50992],"tags":[268435464],"category":0,"game_modes":[1],"keywords":[832],"genres":[8],"first_release_date":852076800000,"platforms":[32],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":32,"date":852076800000,"region":8,"human":"1997-Jan-01","y":1997,"m":1}],"screenshots":[{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/uthdzcdg06zxdtrf9fj5.jpg","cloudinary_id":"uthdzcdg06zxdtrf9fj5","width":704,"height":448},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/rj8grloa2icb5jmv7cip.jpg","cloudinary_id":"rj8grloa2icb5jmv7cip","width":704,"height":448}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/t33iqfzokcroli5lfomf.jpg","cloudinary_id":"t33iqfzokcroli5lfomf","width":300,"height":420},"websites":[{"category":2,"url":"http://nid.wikia.com/wiki/Christmas_Nights_into_Dreams"}]},{"id":45502,"name":"Victory Boxing","slug":"victory-boxing","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/victory-boxing","created_at":1499508846876,"updated_at":1500536691340,"summary":"Your goal is to topple the Champ, a perfect fighter who was born to become the heavyweight champion of the world. But, you must defeat 30 Chumps to get to the Champ, and they won't go down without a fight. Work on your jabs, hooks, and uppercuts along with your blocking and footwork. Master the devastating multi-hit combos, and you just might have a shot at the Champ. But will you be good enough?","popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[46820,39665,101684,101567,101100,100907,100887,100879,100863,100832],"tags":[268435470],"category":0,"genres":[14],"first_release_date":823132800000,"platforms":[32],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":32,"date":823132800000,"region":8,"human":"1996-Feb-01","y":1996,"m":2}]},{"id":45503,"name":"Black Dawn","slug":"b