en parasite and members of the search team have to figure out what is happening and how to stop it! \n \n The game is played via a third person view which is just behind the character and you look over his shoulder. The game is based underwater in a submarine so the developers have added a claustrophobic feeling by giving some areas a limited amount of air so you have to run through to activate the air circulation system. Controls are your typical Resident Evil style which is you pull the Right shoulder button to draw your gun, your d-pad to aim and then a button to shoot. Along your journey of the submarine, you will need to find objects such as keycards to unlock doors and better weapons.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[25646,7329,13189,44076,26914,25300,47823,15830,29525,23175],"tags":[1,19,268435487,536871470,536871945,536872010,536872032,536872211,536872232,536872234,536872647,536872748,536873973,536874727,536875055,536875081,536875094,536875261,536875271,536875483,536875549,536875574,536875852,536875951,536876631,536876687,536876737,536877040,536877264,536877666,536880256,536880642,536881061,536882733],"category":0,"keywords":[558,1033,1098,1120,1299,1320,1322,1735,1836,3061,3815,4143,4169,4182,4349,4359,4571,4637,4662,4940,5039,5719,5775,5825,6128,6352,6754,9344,9730,10149,11821],"themes":[1,19],"genres":[31],"first_release_date":901756800000,"platforms":[32],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":32,"date":901756800000,"region":8,"human":"1998-Jul-30","y":1998,"m":7}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/hydzwanwpjrncdea7oye.jpg","cloudinary_id":"hydzwanwpjrncdea7oye","width":1430,"height":1405}},{"id":46058,"name":"Dark Savior","slug":"dark-savior","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/dark-savior","created_at":1499529691006,"updated_at":1500536671293,"summary":"Put on your thinking caps and prepare to face fierce enemies! Assume the role of Garian, a sword-wielding warrior in search of his escaped prisoner, Bilan. Discover hidden treasures as you explore amazing 3D environments while navigating through a series of mind-melting puzzles!","popularity":1.333333333333333,"category":0,"themes":[1],"genres":[12],"first_release_date":851904000000,"platforms":[32],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":32,"date":851904000000,"region":8,"human":"1996-Dec-30","y":1996,"m":12}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/srihedrgcejihoh8pgmm.jpg","cloudinary_id":"srihedrgcejihoh8pgmm","width":1491,"height":2175}},{"id":46059,"name":"Shining Wisdom","slug":"shining-wisdom","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/shining-wisdom","created_at":1499529937037,"updated_at":1515698603809,"summary":"Once, long ago, a fearsome giant known as the \"Dark Titan\" rose from the abyss and nearly destroyed all Palacia before being bound by magic. Now, the Black Elf Pazort is scheming to rule the world by returning the Dark Titan from the depths of the abyss! But, there is hope. Mars, the son of the legendary warrior Jiles, begins his service in the King's guard at castle Odegan this very day. Guide him through the terrifying traps and devious dungeons as you struggle to seal the Four Elementals that can power Pazort's scheme! Your journey will not be easy. The Lily Pads of Sudden Discomfort lie near every watery path. Rainbow Stinger Scorpions block critical junctions. And, Pazort himself waits in the dank depths of the Catacomb Marsh, guarding the rising Titan. To succeed, you must wield special weapons, items, and power orbs with skill never before witnessed in the land. And succeed you must, for failure will result in the end of all mankind, and the loss of that important victory smooch from the princess.","collection":2155,"popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[12632,36926,36608,16468,47823,19333,26766,25300,59516,27209],"tags":[1,268435468,536871139,536871208,536871938],"category":0,"keywords":[227,296,1026],"themes":[1],"genres":[12],"first_release_date":838339200000,"platforms":[32],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":32,"date":838339200000,"region":8,"human":"1996-Jul-26","y":1996,"m":7}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/me3hf8vfrwrqveggfujw.jpg","cloudinary_id":"me3hf8vfrwrqveggfujw","width":1407,"height":2385}},{"id":46060,"name":"Shining Force III: Premium Disk","slug":"shining-force-iii-premium-disk","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/shining-force-iii-premium-disk","created_at":1499529938811,"updated_at":1500536672566,"summary":"If you're unfamiliar with Shining Force III, or just not a fan, the Premium Disc will have little significance to you. If you are a fan, however, the Shining Force III Premium Disc is likely the greatest and most interesting bonus disc released for a game to date.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"category":0,"genres":[12,15],"first_release_date":915321600000,"platforms":[32],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":32,"date":915321600000,"region":8,"human":"1999-Jan-03","y":1999,"m":1}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/u4wcqnxvdv8veprwd2fd.jpg","cloudinary_id":"u4wcqnxvdv8veprwd2fd","width":1669,"height":1407}},{"id":46061,"name":"Shining Force III: 3rd Scenario","slug":"shining-force-iii-3rd-scenario","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/shining-force-iii-3rd-scenario","created_at":1499529943141,"updated_at":1500536673424,"summary":"Scenario 3, Bulzome Rising, stars Julian, a mercenary who appears as a secondary character in both Scenario 1 and Scenario 2. He is for all intents and purposes the true main character of Shining Force III. His initial motivation as the story begins is to track down and kill Galm, one of, if not the, most powerful member of the Vandals, a powerful race of beings that existed over 1,000 years ago. Julian believes that Galm killed his father and is seeking revenge. This story arc is first introduced in an earlier Shining game, Shining the Holy Ark, in which Julian appears as a young boy who asks the party to search for his missing father. \n \nJulian joins Synbios in the midst of his quest in Scenario 1, but after an encounter with Galm, he is tossed over a waterfall at the suspension bridge and believed by Synbios' army to be dead. He reappears in Scenario 2, apparently washing ashore at the site of a battle between Medion's army and the Bulzome Sect. Knowing the sect's ties to the Vandals, Julian agrees to fight alongside Medion. As it becomes clear that the sect is trying to kill Gracia, a child intended to become the next Innovator (A Shining Series figure equatable to a god), Julian takes on the task of protecting him and helping him realize his destiny. \n \nScenario 3 starts about 60% through scenario 2's story, and focuses primarily on battles against the Bulzome Sect and their allies in both Aspinia and Destonia. While scenarios 1 \u0026 2 happen at roughly the same time, much of scenario 3 takes place after both, but there is some \"overlap\". Eventually Julian leads a three-party coalition consisting of the armies of both Synbios and Medion, to engage in the final conflict against Bulzome, a powerful Vandal long sealed in another dimension, and the true orchestrator of the conflict.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"category":0,"genres":[12,15],"first_release_date":909100800000,"platforms":[32],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":32,"date":909100800000,"region":8,"human":"1998-Oct-23","y":1998,"m":10}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/dqujkv9kgwqpz1kxzwnd.jpg","cloudinary_id":"dqujkv9kgwqpz1kxzwnd","width":1424,"height":1397}},{"id":46062,"name":"Shining Force III: 2nd Scenario","slug":"shining-force-iii-2nd-scenario","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/shining-force-iii-2nd-scenario","created_at":1499529944808,"updated_at":1513086821367,"summary":"Scenario 2, Target: Child of God, features Medion, Prince of Destonia, and youngest of three sons of Emperor Domaric. Although loyal to his father and his country, he senses that there are other forces at work beneath the tensions between Aspinia and Destonia. He attends the conference in Saraband on behalf of Destonia, along with his brothers Arrawnt and Mageron. As discovered in Scenario 1, much of this influence comes from the Bulzome sect, as well as collaborating separatist factions within both Destonia and Aspinia. Medion works parallel to Synbios of Aspinia, often disposing of rogue Aspinian elements to spare Synbios's force from fighting against its own countrymen. At the end of the game, Medion is forced to battle with Synbios' force when Julian steps in to stop them.","collection":578,"popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[26766,12632,36926,36534,18398,17583,75813,25921,19698,25311],"tags":[268435468,268435471,536871208,536871938,536875472,536880261,536881157],"category":0,"keywords":[296,1026,4560,9349,10245],"genres":[12,15],"first_release_date":896400000000,"platforms":[32],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":32,"date":896400000000,"region":8,"human":"1998-May-29","y":1998,"m":5}],"alternative_names":[{"name":"Shining Force III Scenario 2: Nerawareta Miko","comment":"Other"},{"name":"Shining Force III Scenario 2: Target: Child of God","comment":"Other"}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/assfknrfg0buwjf1wp2c.jpg","cloudinary_id":"assfknrfg0buwjf1wp2c","width":1419,"height":1406}},{"id":46063,"name":"Shining the Holy Ark","slug":"shining-the-holy-ark","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/shining-the-holy-ark","created_at":1499529948507,"updated_at":1516162760470,"summary":"As the capable mercenary Arthur, you must summon every ounce of your role-playing prowess and lead your comrades on a do-or-die hunt for the kingdom's sacred artifacts. It's the RPG you've been waiting for, loaded with enough Medieval monsters and challenging \"four character\" control to stretch your role playing skills far beyond your wildest imagination.","collection":2155,"popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[26766,36926,36534,18398,19333,11214,47823,25300,1263