d and shown a top-down map of BusyTown and using a whirlwind can interact with various objects on the screen to view animations. \nAdditionally, the player can choose these different locations at the main screen that has the player become Lowly the Worm and fly around the map using his Apple Helicopter. It also features many the characters from Scarry's educational books.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[34218,34919,36608,16468,51464,59516,66034,65125,23175,28029],"tags":[1,34,536871446,536872216,536874653,536875054,536875096,536876672,536877325],"category":0,"keywords":[534,1304,3741,4142,4184,5760,6413],"themes":[1,34],"first_release_date":760060800000,"platforms":[29],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":29,"date":760060800000,"region":8,"human":"1994-Feb-01","y":1994,"m":2}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/z3sqwghngtdyyshi2cbo.jpg","cloudinary_id":"z3sqwghngtdyyshi2cbo","width":640,"height":480}},{"id":46203,"name":"R.B.I. Baseball '93","slug":"rbi-baseball-93","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/rbi-baseball-93","created_at":1499541504499,"updated_at":1515777875040,"summary":"Play is either player vs computer, as either the home or visiting team, two players, or computer vs computer. Password saves allowing resuming the multi-game modes. Included is the ability to edit the teams; you can transfer players between teams to keep the rosters current, or just have some fun. Finally, the Game Breaker mode allows setting up a game in progress using any team, any inning, any score.","collection":785,"popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[46261,48253,72798,73032,44735,18416,69259,22690,67805,46546],"tags":[268435470,536870932,536872078,536875562,536875570,536876165,536878341],"category":0,"keywords":[20,1166,4650,4658,5253,7429],"genres":[14],"first_release_date":728524800000,"platforms":[29],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":29,"date":728524800000,"region":8,"human":"1993-Feb-01","y":1993,"m":2}],"alternative_names":[{"na